# Cross-package deps use the `workspace:^` protocol, which always links locally and is
# rewritten to a real semver range at publish time. That needs no configuration here —
# and `npm` warns on pnpm-only keys, so this file stays empty of them.

# Publishing / provenance (TODO): when npm publishing runs from CI with an OIDC-enabled
# workflow, enable provenance here or pass `--provenance` at publish time:
#
#   provenance=true
#
# Do NOT put an auth token in this file. CI should inject one at runtime, e.g.
#   //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
# with NODE_AUTH_TOKEN coming from the CI secret store.
